"{\"uid\": \"democracynow.org-2024-7-22-headlines-afp_journalist_christina_assi_carries_olympic_torch_to_honor_slain_and_wounded_media_workers\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"In this age of widespread misinformation and increased threats to press freedom, support for independent journalism is more important than ever.Media isessentialto the functioning of a democratic society.Please donate today, so we can keep delivering urgent reporting on the world's most pressing issues.Every dollar makes a difference.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 336, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Thank you so much!Democracy Now!Amy Goodman  In this age of widespread misinformation and increased threats to press freedom, support for independent journalism is more important than ever.Media isessentialto the functioning of a democratic society.Please donate today, so we can keep delivering urgent reporting on the world's most pressing issues.Every dollar makes a difference.\", \"from\": 337, \"to\": 718, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Thank you so much!Democracy Now!Amy Goodman  We rely on contributions from you, our viewers and listeners to do our work.\", \"from\": 719, \"to\": 840, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you visit us daily or weekly or even just once a month, now is a great time to make your monthly contribution.\", \"from\": 841, \"to\": 954, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please do your part today.\", \"from\": 956, \"to\": 982, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Lebanese photojournalist Christina Assi of Agence France-Presse carried the Olympic torch in Paris on Sunday to honor journalists wounded or killed on the job.\", \"from\": 984, \"to\": 1147, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 988, \"end\": 996, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lebanese_people\", \"score\": 0.544186672236688, \"rank\": 0.8374235700412531, \"text\": \"Lebanese\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lebanese_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/re